headline: STXS Partners With CardioFocus to Boost Robotic Pulsed Field Ablation
summary: Stereotaxis partners with CardioFocus to commercialize the first robotic Pulsed Field Ablation system, aiming to revolutionize cardiac arrhythmia treatment.
